          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1708343709858-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a low heat</p><p>Once melted, remove the pot from the heat and add your <strong>Henderson's relish</strong>, <strong>sriracha</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Stir everything together until it combines and becomes a sauce-like consistency – this is your<strong> buffalo sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1708343713460-x200.jpg",
